To achieve that, we can use the Component Namespace Data & Component Namespace Life Cycle Callback feature of fractal-component. When we create the ComponentManager using new ComponentManager() method, we can opt to register namespaceInitCallback & namespaceDestroyCallback through ManageableComponentOptions.

